metadata.name: White
metadata.description: The DFox Fan Passes are a collection of exclusive non-fungible tokens (NFTs) that give holders access to a range of special perks and benefits within DeAaron Fox's fan interaction platform. There are three tiers of NFT tokens available: White, Metal & Black. Each tier provides a different level of access to experiences and merchandise, and all holders are eligible to earn $FOX tokens through staking mechanism available on the platform. With a DFox Fan Pass, fans can get closer to their favorite athlete and unlock a whole new world of exclusive experiences and rewards.
